## Operational memory (not the same as vector lane)

| Table | Role |
|-------|------|
| `agentsam_memory` | Structured key/value memory (fact/preference/project/…); has `d1_id` sync — **primary operational store** |
| `agentsam_memory_oai3large_1536` | Embeddings for memory **retrieval** |

